data.description: Welcome to this exceptional Northside family home! Boasting 4 beds and 2.5 baths, this residence is designed for both comfortable living and entertaining. The brand new deck and new exterior and interior paint enhance the curb appeal and overall charm of the property. Step inside and discover a spacious haven for family and guests. Whether you're grilling on the brand new deck or preparing meals in the open kitchen, enjoying a football game in the large family room, or hosting events in the spacious backyard, you'll always have the perfect space for family and guests. The master bedroom offers generous space, and the basement boasts two bonus rooms, providing flexibility for various needs. As if that weren't enough, this home is situated in an established neighborhood close to shopping, with easy access to both Highway 50 and I-25. And there's more good news! A unique feature awaits in the garage – a rock wall, adding a touch of character and versatility to the space. Don't miss the opportunity to experience this well-appointed home for yourself. Schedule a viewing and discover the perfect blend of comfort and style!
